{"name":{"entry":102,"name":"At-Takathur","meaning":"The Rivalry in world increase"},"verses":[{"arabic":" أَلْهَىٰكُمُ ٱلتَّكَاثُرُ","translation":"The mutual rivalry for piling up (the good things of this world) diverts you (from the more serious things),","transliteration":"Alhakumu attakathur"},{"arabic":"حَتَّىٰ زُرْتُمُ ٱلْمَقَابِرَ","translation":"Until ye visit the graves.","transliteration":"Hatta zurtumu almaqabir"},{"arabic":"كَلَّا سَوْفَ تَعْلَمُونَ","translation":"But nay, ye soon shall know (the reality).","transliteration":"Kalla sawfa taAAlamoon"},{"arabic":"ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَوْفَ تَعْلَمُونَ","translation":"Again, ye soon shall know!","transliteration":"Thumma kalla sawfa taAAlamoon"},{"arabic":"كَلَّا لَوْ تَعْلَمُونَ عِلْمَ ٱلْيَقِينِ","translation":"Nay, were ye to know with certainty of mind, (ye would beware!)","transliteration":"Kalla law taAAlamoona AAilma alyaqeen"},{"arabic":"لَتَرَوُنَّ ٱلْجَحِيمَ","translation":"Ye shall certainly see Hell-Fire!","transliteration":"Latarawunna aljaheem"},{"arabic":"ثُمَّ لَتَرَوُنَّهَا عَيْنَ ٱلْيَقِينِ","translation":"Again, ye shall see it with certainty of sight!","transliteration":"Thumma latarawunnaha AAayna alyaqeen"},{"arabic":"ثُمَّ لَتُسْـَٔلُنَّ يَوْمَئِذٍ عَنِ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","translation":"Then, shall ye be questioned that Day about the joy (ye indulged in!).","transliteration":"Thumma latus-alunna yawma-ithin AAaniannaAAeem"}]}